channel.title: [539] Codeusa
channel.description:
(Names not official but I don't feel like coming up with one atm.
Revision: 539 Why?: Because I found the cache on one of my players computers. Who's on the team: Me & Impulser. What is the base?: [s]Hyperion[/s] After Impulser pestering me about it, we converted all work over to rs2hd. It works better & runs faster.
January 15th: Started Login Set window pane set tabs Send string send info rendering landscape rendering packet handling fixed a flicker bug [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/2Pfsq.png[/img]
January 16th: [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/2UJ2Z.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/yOaz5.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/oUEMe.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/6HzoL.png[/img] That's it for today, going to get multiplayer & private chat working tonight or tomorrow
Overall goals: most if not all skills working bosses minigames a combat system to surpass my current servers all that good stuff.
Things i will not be adding: Customs Newer Items New prayers Custom sprites (besides login background) "training areas" "skilling areas"
If you want any of that go play any other server that is currently out or RuneScape.
[QUOTE]January 17th- 18th updates to come find hit updates make a basic npc combat just to test make a basic pvp forum integration (will only take a few seconds with my scripting system) Hiscores (easiest thing to to do) Update server (already done just need to implement it for this revision) Multiplayer Pm [/QUOTE] [img]http://i.imgur.com/R63v9.png[/img] multiplayer [img]http://i.imgur.com/66iPf.jpg[/img] pm Clan chat [img]http://i.imgur.com/XxfzL.png[/img]
Doing npc combat next
